Authors@R: person(c("Paul", "J."), "Northrop", email = "p.northrop@ucl.ac.uk",
  role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Provides R code, datasets and vignettes to help students taking 
  STAT0002 Introduction to Probability and Statistics at University College 
  London to understand the course material and to see how R can be used to 
  perform some of the analyses in the course.
